{"tid":2236942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"閻麗夢博士中文解釋第二份報告的來龍去脈","createTime":"2020-10-10T01:04:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T01:14:20.000Z","uid":294518,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"376fcf9c79ed993526c5dbc82892f05960ff15ef","tid":2236942,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T01:04:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VAKlS2oM9EU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVAKlS2oM9EU&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzhdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=684f719d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VAKlS2oM9EU</a>"},{"pid":"33748504d08e4b18f7b168f32954ad19b22e1d44","tid":2236942,"uid":294518,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T01:07:03.000Z","msg":"戰斗室採訪閆博士：<br />\n1, 我想介紹一下這個新概念 - 超限生化武器。它遠超傳統意義上的生化武器，來自於中共國軍科醫學研究院，即中共國軍事科學院,軍事醫學研究院。<br />\n2, 只要有中共軍方的病毒骨架, 也就是舟山蝙蝠冠狀病毒, 他們可以輕易在實驗室製造出SARS-CoV-2, (1/5)<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/billowypie/status/1314424777302437888?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbillowypie%2Fstatus%2F1314424777302437888%3Fs%3D20&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzhdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&h=f9450f1a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbillowypie%2Fstatus%2F1314424777302437888%3Fs%3D20&h=e0658acd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/billowypie/status/1314424777302437888?s=20</a>"},{"pid":"26277a935a1ec7c0bf1dc105ca02c70ab1db06a8","tid":2236942,"uid":294518,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T01:08:00.000Z","msg":"並且,這是一場大規模、有組織的造假行為, 涉及了整個科學界以及同行評審的期刊。他們幫助了中國共產黨。<br />\n3, 最後我想告訴大家的是: 這是一個生化武器， 而且是一個現代化的超限生化武器。所以大家要明白，我們現在正遭受超限生化戰的荼毒，超限生物戰已經攻陷了整個世界。<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/billowypie/status/1314424786945142785?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fbillowypie%2Fstatus%2F1314424786945142785%3Fs%3D20&d=6zgGjWaceJ4ICz2LU8gYzhdm8TOyDCEw47gAfDhO9KY%3D&